-- Nagarjuna Fertilizers May Set up Urea Plant in Nigeria, Standard Reports
-- Pratik Parija
-- 2010-07-18T03:57:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-18/nagarjuna-fertilizers-may-set-up-urea-plant-in-nigeria-standard-reports.html

          
          
             Nagarjuna Fertilizers and Chemicals
Ltd. may invest 50 billion rupees ($1.06 billion) to set up a 1
million ton urea plant in Nigeria with a local partner, the
Business Standard reported, citing Chairman K.S. Raju.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
